OL,6,FAlongside a BAFTA and Pulitzer Prize,
OL,7,FChernov also won in the Best
OL,8,FDocumentary category at the Academy
OL,9,FAwards on Sunday.
OL,11,FIn his acceptance speech, Chernov told
OL,12,Fa star-studded crowd in Los Angeles:
OL,13,F"I am honoured but I will probably be
OL,14,Fthe first director on this stage to
OL,15,Fsay that I wish I had never made this
OL,16,Ffilm."
