OL,3,C20 Days in Mariupol: Nurse recounts
OL,4,Cfinal days before Russian occupation
OL,6,FFor Olena, the movie is an important
OL,7,Freminder to the world of a war that is
OL,8,Fvery much still ongoing - and a time
OL,9,Fin her life that is now forever etched
OL,10,Fin memory.
OL,12,FSpeaking to ITV News exclusively from
OL,13,Fher new home in the eastern city of
OL,14,FDnipro, Olena says the death of the
OL,15,Ffour-year-old girl was a "turning
OL,16,Fpoint" for the team of doctors
OL,17,FMariupol Regional Hospital.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G4/14
