OL,3,C20 Days in Mariupol: Nurse recounts
OL,4,Cfinal days before Russian occupation
OL,6,FOne day, the team raided a nearby
OL,7,Fpharmacy to stock up on equipment.
OL,8,FWhen it snowed, they collected snow
OL,9,Finto containers and melted it so they
OL,10,F"could at least wash our hands" before
OL,11,Fmedical procedures.
OL,13,FOlena said she constantly thought
OL,14,Fabout evacuating her family but that
OL,15,Fthey "didn't have the opportunity" to.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G8/14
