OL,3,C20 Days in Mariupol: Nurse recounts
OL,4,Cfinal days before Russian occupation
OL,6,FTwenty-five tense Russian checkpoints
OL,7,Flater, they were out. Her only thought
OL,8,F- "I want to wish that other people
OL,9,Fnever experience something like this."
OL,11,FThe Oscar win is a first for Ukrainian
OL,12,Fcinema, and for a film that documented
OL,13,Fthe horrors of the war at its peak. It
OL,14,Fhas reminded viewers of the
OL,15,Fcatastrophic scenes civilians were
OL,16,Ffaced with.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G11/14
