OL,3,C20 Days in Mariupol: Nurse recounts
OL,4,Cfinal days before Russian occupation
OL,6,FMost of her colleagues have also
OL,7,Fcontinued working, but in Kyiv, in a
OL,8,Fnewly opened medical clinic named
OL,9,Fafter Mariupol - in memory of their
OL,10,Fcity, which is still under Russian
OL,11,Foccupation.JEvery time an air raid
OL,12,Fsiren sounds, her mind brings her back
OL,13,Fto March 2022.
OL,15,FShe has no intention of returning,
OL,16,Fsaying: "Maybe in my heart I want to
OL,17,Freturn, but in my mind I don't.
OL,18,FBecause it is a dead city. So many
OL,19,Fpeople died there that its probably
OL,20,Fimpossible to count."
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G13/14
